*time step (ms): *   - Lignes starting with a * character are ignored by stimseq
*   - Empty Lines are ignored by stimseq
*   - Comment column can be left empty with or without a final comma.
*     The parser of stimseq will handle it
*   - Columns V1 to V8 and piezo will accept 0 for false and 1 for true. Any value above 1 will be treated as a one.
